body:
This question is better asked on  [StackOverflow](http://stackoverflow.com/questions/tagged/tensorflow) since it is not a  bug or feature request. There is also a larger community that reads questions there. Thanks!

(That said, in this case the files you're looking at are produced by [`tf.train.Saver`](https://www.tensorflow.org/api_docs/python/tf/train/Saver) - whose documentation will describe the process of exporting and importing tensor contents a bit).

Hope that helps.
